      • startGUIRefresh

        public void startGUIRefresh(int refreshRateInMilliSeconds)
        Starts the GUI refresh function. Time in milli seconds. Times smaller 50 ms are not provided. NOTICE!!!!!!!!!!!!! supported int values: Vertical: range 0-100; Horizontal: range 0-100; Gripper: 0 = open; 1 = closed; UltraSonic: 0 = free; 1 = occupied;
        Parameters:
        refreshRateInMilliSeconds -
